{"type": "article", "id": 28133, "title": "平衡座椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-14T06:41:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142452sL0eNdWZxOj6iYBl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>为了适应越来越多变的办公环境，洛杉矶的设计工作室 Box Clever 最近为家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.knoll.com/\">Knoll</a> 设计了一款名为 HiLo 的平衡座椅。它可以根据人的身高和桌子的高度进行调节，稳定的底座能使人在保持平衡的同时自然倾斜，提供了一种更健康的转换姿势的方式。HiLo 目前还未投入生产，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.knoll.com/product/hilo\">链接</a>订阅产品的最新进展。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021424500IjOZpL4cyMWoXb3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.24327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142450eUPmXOqaDFzJjBop.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68704156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142451oUGSZDVRTXgNrIni.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26283619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}